description: Bring home the famous taste of Rao’s Homemade Roasted Garlic Pizza Sauce. Rao’s Homemade Roasted Garlic Pizza Sauce is a premium, carb conscious pizza sauce made with only the finest ingredients. Each batch of Rao’s Homemade Pizza Sauce is slow-cooked in small batches with high quality ingredients. These wholesome ingredients blend sweet Italian tomatoes, olive oil, and onions with fresh basil, fresh garlic, oregano, black pepper and salt creating a pizza sauce that brings back memories of family dinners around the table.
